t: "On that Day hypocrite men and women will beg the believers, ‚ÄúWait for us so that we may have some of your light.‚ÄĚ It will be said ňĻmockinglyňļ, ‚ÄúGo back ňĻto the worldňļ and seek a light ňĻthereňļ!‚ÄĚ Then a ňĻseparatingňļ wall with a gate will be erected between them. On the near side will be grace and on the far side will be torment"